<mxfile host="Electron" agent="Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) draw.io/29.2.9 Chrome/140.0.7339.249 Electron/38.7.2 Safari/537.36" version="29.2.9">
  <diagram name="Page-1" id="nEjSzRWqN_9rVFnFuiG8">
    <mxGraphModel dx="3203" dy="1650" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <mxCell id="c4LFta7eevNrK4IFVKi2-18" edge="1" parent="1" source="ML2OlnQcUtptjyXd42Cn-2" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="ML2OlnQcUtptjyXd42Cn-19">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <mxPoint x="159" y="2132" as="sourcePoint" />
            <mxPoint x="218.99999999999977" y="2132" as="targetPoint" />
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="c4LFta7eevNrK4IFVKi2-1" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="Q1. System Design Question&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Design an Online Learning Platform (similar to Coursera / Udemy) with the following services:&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;User Login Service&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Course Enrollment Service&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Course Search Service&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Video Lecture Streaming Service&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Additional Requirements&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Optimize the platform using a CDC (Change Data Capture) Pipeline for tracking course progress and analytics.&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Highlight where the Proxy Design Pattern can be used in the system.&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Use HLS (HTTP Live Streaming) or DASH streaming for adaptive video playback along with the manifest file." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="460" width="560" x="260" y="20" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="c4LFta7eevNrK4IFVKi2-2" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;Functional Requirements&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="290" x="260" y="510" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="c4LFta7eevNrK4IFVKi2-4" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="User Authentication&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Users platform par register aur login kar sakte hain.&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Authentication JWT / session based ho sakta hai.&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Course Search&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Users keyword, category, instructor ke basis par courses search kar sakte hain.&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Fast searching ke liye Search Service + Indexing (ElasticSearch) use ho sakta hai.&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Course Enrollment&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Users course select karke enroll kar sakte hain.&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Enrollment data Enrollment Service + Database me store hoga.&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Video Lecture Streaming&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Platform video lectures provide karega.&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;HLS / DASH streaming ke through adaptive bitrate streaming hogi.&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Course Progress Tracking&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;System user ka lecture progress, completion percentage track karega.&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;CDC pipeline analytics system ko updates bhejega." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="640" width="470" x="270" y="560" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="c4LFta7eevNrK4IFVKi2-5" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;Non-Functional Requirements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="50" width="410" x="290" y="1260" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="c4LFta7eevNrK4IFVKi2-6" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="1. Scalability:&#xa;200–300M users. Assume the platform contains around 50K courses with ~500K video lectures (~1 hour each).&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;2. CAP Theorem: Availability &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Consistency&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Availability in watching course lectures and streaming educational videos.&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Consistency in course enrollment, payments, and certification records.&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;3. Latency:&#xa;50 – 100 ms&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Client should be able to start and watch video lectures with zero or negligible buffering using adaptive streaming (HLS/DASH)." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="310" width="560" x="295" y="1320" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
